Bxc4 e6 7. O-O Be7 8. Nbd2 Bb7 9. Be2 Nbd7 10. Nc4 c5 11. Nfe5 O-O 12. dxc5
Nxe5 13. Nxe5 Qc7 14. c6 Rad8 15. Qc2 Bd6 16. f4 Ba8 17. Bf3 Bxe5 18. fxe5 Nd5
19. Qc5 {Krykun,Y (2236)-Christiansen,J (2391) Porec 2015 0-1 (53)}) 5. Bxc4 a6
$146 {Prevents intrusion on b5} (5... e6 6. Nc3 a6 7. e4 b5 8. Bd3 Nb4 9. Bb1
c5 10. a3 cxd4 11. Qxd4 Qxd4 12. Nxd4 e5 13. axb4 exd4 14. Nxb5 Bxb4+ 15. Ke2
