is interesting}) 19. Kd2 $16 Qe7 $4 {causes even greater problems} (19... Bd7
$5 $16) 20. Re1 (20. Qc3+ $5 {and White can already relax} Kg8 21. Rxh6 Qxe3+
22. Kc2 Qf2+ 23. Kb1 Qd4 24. Qxd4 cxd4 25. fxg5 Re3 $18) 20... Rf8 (20... Qf6
21. Reh1 Rh8 22. fxg5 Qxg5 23. Rh5 Qxg3 24. Qc3+ Qe5 25. Qxe5+ dxe5 26. Bxf5
Bxf5 27. Rxf5 $18) 21. Qc3+ Kg6 $4 {shortens the misery for Black} (21... Qf6
22. Qxf6+ Rxf6 23. fxg5 hxg5 $18) 22. Reh1 (22. e4 {seems even better} Qf6 23.
exf5+ Kg7 24. Re7+ Kg8 25. Qxf6 Rxf6 26. fxg5 hxg5 27. Re8+ Kg7 $18) 22... Qh7
(22... Qg7 {cannot change destiny} 23. Qxg7+ Kxg7 24. Rxh6 $18) 23. g4 (23.
