Nc6 5. Bc4 Nf6 $146 {Black has a cramped position. Black's pieces can't move:
c8+f8} (5... e6 6. f4 (6. Nge2 Nf6 7. O-O a6 8. a3 b5 9. Ba2 Bb7 10. Bf4 Be7
11. Ng3 d6 12. Qe2 O-O 13. Rfd1 Qb8 14. Rd2 Ne5 15. Rad1 Qc7 16. Bg5 Rfd8 17.
