16. Rac1 Rfd8 17. h3 Rac8 18. Qc2 Na5 19. d5 exd5 {Milov,V (2676)-Landa,K 
(2678) Ajaccio 2007 0-1 (45)}) (5. Ne5 O-O 6. Bg5 c5 7. Rc1 Nc6 8. e3 cxd4 9.
