{Black has a mate threat} 23. Rf1 Qxb2 24. Qxe6 Qxa2 {Black has a new
protected passed pawn: c6} (24... a5 25. Qe3+ Ka6 26. a3 $17) 25. Qe3+ c5 (
25... Kb5 26. Qe7 b6 27. Qxg7 $11) 26. Qe6+ $11 Kb5 27. Qe8+ Kb4 28. Qg6 {
