Kb5 31. Qe8+ $11) 28... Rd7 (28... b5 29. Qxg7 c4 30. Rc1 $11) 29. Qg4+ $11 {
White forks: d7} Rd4 {Black threatens to win material: Rd4xg4. Here comes the
goal-getter} 30. Qxg7 b6 31. Qe7 Kb3 (31... Kb5 32. Qe8+ Ka6 33. g3 $11) 32.
Qe3+ (32. h4 c4 33. h5 Qc2 34. Qxa7 Rd1 35. Qxb6+ Ka2 36. Qa5+ Kb3 37. Qb5+ Ka2
