Kb5 36. Qe8+ Ka6 37. f5 $18) 34... Kc4 $4 {ruins a clearly superior position} (
34... c4 $142 {is just about the only chance} 35. Qe4 Qb2 $11) 35. Qe4+ (35.
Qe6+ $142 {might be the shorter path} Rd5 36. Rd1 $18) 35... Kc3 $4 {the final
mistake, not that it matters anymore} (35... Kb5 36. f5 Rb2 $18) 36. f5 (36.
Rf3+ Kb2 37. Qe5+ Kb1 38. Qe1+ Kc2 39. Qxd2+ Kxd2 40. Rf2+ Ke3 41. Rxa2 Ke4 42.
