{D35: Queen's Gambit Declined: Exchange Variation} 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 d5
4. c5 (4. Qa4+ Bd7 5. Qb3 dxc4 6. Qxc4 Be7 7. Nf3 O-O 8. Bf4 Na6 9. Rd1 c5 10.
