threatens to win material: h6xg5} 17. Bd2 Nh7 (17... g5 $5 $11 {is an
interesting idea}) 18. Qe3 $16 g5 19. Qd3 (19. Ne2 Nf6 20. Nd4 Kg6 $16) 19...
Qe6 (19... Nf6 20. Ne2 $16) 20. b3 (20. Ne2 Nf6 $16) 20... f5 $14 21. f3 f4 {
Black gains space} 22. Ne2 h5 {[%cal Yg5g4] Black prepares the advance g4} (
