1999 1-0 (32)}) (9... dxc4 10. Bxc4 b5 11. Be2 $11) 10. Rc1 Ne8 11. Bxe7 {
White forks: f8+d8} Qxe7 12. Re1 f5 13. a3 Nef6 14. Nd2 Qh7 15. cxd5 exd5 16.
f3 {Covers e4+g4} Re8 17. e4 fxe4 (17... Nb6 $5 $16) 18. fxe4 dxe4 19. Ncxe4
Rf8 20. Qb3+ Kh8 (20... Nd5 21. Nf3 $16) 21. Nd6 $18 Nb6 22. Rf1 {White has a
very active position} (22. Nf3 Nfd5 $18) 22... Nbd5 $2 {A valuable piece} (
22... Bg4 23. Bc2 $14) 23. h4 (23. N2c4 Nd7 $18) 23... h5 $2 (23... Qc7 24.
N2c4 Kg7 $16) 24. N2e4 $4 {White has let it slip away} (24. N2c4 Be6 25. Rce1
Bg8 $18) 24... Qh6 $4 (24... Qe7 $142 $11 {and Black can hope to live}) 25. Ng5
$18 Qg7 26. Qc2 (26. Nc4 $142 Bf5 27. Bxf5 gxf5 28. Ne6 $18) 26... Bf5 $4 {
cause more grief} (26... Ne3 $142 27. Qc5 Bg4 $16) 27. Bxf5 $18 Nh7 (27... gxf5
{hardly improves anything} 28. Qxf5 Qc7 $18) 28. Rce1 (28. Ngf7+ $142 {and
White can celebrate victory} Rxf7 29. Nxf7+ Qxf7 30. Bxg6 $18) 28... Qxd4+ (
28... Nxg5 29. hxg5 Qxd4+ 30. Qf2 Qxf2+ 31. Rxf2 gxf5 $16) 29. Kh1 (29. Qf2
Qxf2+ 30. Rxf2 Nxg5 31. Bxg6 Rxf2 32. Kxf2 Rf8+ 33. Kg3 $16) 29... Qxh4+ $4 (
29... Nxg5 $142 30. hxg5 Ne3 $11) 30. Kg1 $4 {throws away the game} (30. Bh3
$142 {White has the better game} Qxg5 31. Nf7+ Rxf7 32. Rxf7 $18) 30... Qd4+ $4
{with this move Black loses his initiative} (30... Nxg5 31. Be4 Rxf1+ 32. Rxf1
Nxe4 33. Qxe4 Qxe4 34. Nxe4 $19) 31. Kh1 $2 (31. Qf2 $142 Qxf2+ 32. Rxf2 Nxg5
33. Bxg6 Rxf2 34. Kxf2 Rf8+ 35. Bf5 $17) 31... Ne3 $4 {instead of simply
winning the game} (31... Nxg5 $142 {and Black has reached his goal} 32. Qd3
Qh4+ 33. Bh3 Kh7 $19) 32. Ngf7+ $18 Kg7 (32... Rxf7 {does not win a prize} 33.
Nxf7+ Kg7 34. Rxe3 Qxe3 35. Bxg6 Nf6 $18) 33. Qf2 (33. Rxe3 $142 {makes it
even easier for White} Rxf7 34. Rd3 $18) 33... Nxf5 $4 {but even a better move
would not have saved the game} (33... Rxf7 $142 34. Nxf7 Nxf5 35. Qxd4+ Nxd4
$18) 34. Nxf5+ gxf5 35. Qxd4+ Nf6 36. Rxf5 Rxf7 37. Rxf6 $1 {Deflection: e7}
Rxf6 (37... Rxf6 38. Re7+ {Mate attack Decoy Deflection}) 38. Re7+ Kg6 39. Qe4+
Rf5 40. Rxb7 (40. Re6+ Kg5 41. Qe3+ Rf4 42. Qe5+ Kg4 43. Rg6+ Kh4 44. Qg5#)
40... Raf8 $18 41. Qe6+ R5f6 42. Qe3 R8f7 43. Rxf7 (43. Qxa7 h4 44. Rxf7 Rxf7
$18) 43... Kxf7 (43... Rxf7 {is the last straw} 44. Kh2 Kf5 $18) 44. Qxa7+ Kg6
45. Qe3 Rf5 46. a4 Rf6 47. Qe4+ Kf7 48. Qh7+ Ke6 49. Qxh5 Rf1+ 50. Kh2 Rf5 51.
Qxf5+ $1 {a brilliant end} Kxf5 52. a5 (52. a5 Kg6 53. a6 Kh5 54. a7 Kg5 55.
a8=Q Kg6 56. g4 Kf6 57. Qe8 c5 58. Kg3 c4 59. Kh4 c3 60. bxc3 Kg7 61. Kg5 Kh7
62. Kf6 Kh6 63. Qh8#) 1-0

