$18) 61... Nc6 $11 {The knight blocks c5} 62. Qd3+ Kh8 63. Qe3 Kh7 64. Qd3+ {
Twofold repetition} (64. Rf2 $142 {and the rest is a matter of technique} Qe7
$18) 64... Kh8 65. Kg1 Qf6 (65... Qf4 66. Rg4 Qc1+ 67. Kh2 h5 $18) 66. Rg6 (66.
Qg3 $5 {might be the shorter path} Qf8 67. Qd6 Qxd6 68. cxd6 Kh7 $18) 66...
Qxd4+ 67. Qxd4+ Nxd4 68. Rxh6+ Kg7 69. Rh4 (69. c6 $142 {finishes off the
opponent} Nxc6 70. Rxe6 $18) 69... Nf3+ $19 (69... Nf3+ 70. Kf1 Nxh4 $19) 0-1

