{B51: Sicilian: Moscow Variation (3 Bb5+) without 3...Bd7} 1. e4 c5 2. Nf3 Nc6
3. Bb5 d6 4. Bxc6+ bxc6 5. O-O Bg4 6. Nc3 $146 (6. h3 Bh5 (6... Bxf3 7. Qxf3 e6
8. c3 Be7 9. d4 cxd4 10. cxd4 Nf6 11. Nc3 d5 12. Be3 O-O 13. b3 Bb4 14. Bg5
Bxc3 15. Qxc3 Nxe4 16. Bxd8 Nxc3 17. Be7 Rfe8 18. Bc5 a5 19. f3 a4 20. Kf2 Ra6
21. Rfc1 {Leko,P (2545)-Gelfand,B (2685) Munich 1994 0-1 (42)}) 7. Re1 (7. c3
Nf6 8. Re1 e6 9. d3 Be7 10. Nbd2 O-O 11. Qa4 Qc7 12. e5 Nd5 13. exd6 Bxd6 14.
Qh4 Nf4 15. Ne4 Bxf3 16. Bxf4 Bxf4 17. gxf3 Rad8 18. Nxc5 e5 19. d4 exd4 20.
Re7 Qd6 21. Ne4 Qg6+ {Velicka,P (2420)-Pisk,P (2295) Czechia 1996 1/2-1/2})
7... Nf6 8. d3 e6 9. Nbd2 Nd7 10. Nf1 Be7 11. Ng3 Bg6 12. Bd2 (12. Nh2 Bh4 13.
Bf4 e5 14. Be3 Bxg3 15. fxg3 O-O 16. g4 d5 17. Qf3 dxe4 18. dxe4 Qa5 19. Rad1
Rfd8 20. g5 Qa4 21. Bf2 Qxc2 22. h4 h5 23. gxh6 Nf6 24. Rxd8+ Rxd8 25. hxg7
Nxe4 26. Be3 f5 {Borghi,H (2320)-Soppe,G (2405) San Luis 1990 0-1 (37)}) 12...
h5 13. Ne2 h4 14. Nf4 Bh7 15. e5 d5 16. g4 hxg3 17. fxg3 Qb8 18. b3 g5 19. Ng2
Bg8 20. Bxg5 Bxg5 {Titov,G (2200)-Yudasin,L (2475) Kostroma 1985 0-1 (39)}) (6.
c3 Nf6 7. Re1 e6 8. d4 Bxf3 9. Qxf3 cxd4 10. cxd4 d5 11. e5 Nd7 12. Qg3 Qb6 13.
Rd1 g6 14. Nc3 Be7 15. Bh6 Qxb2 16. Rab1 Qa3 17. Rd3 Qa6 18. Rf3 Bf8 19. Qf4
Bxh6 20. Qxh6 Qc4 {Velicka,P (2335)-Videki,S (2385) Zalakaros 1991 1/2-1/2 (64)
}) (6. h3 Bh5 $14) 6... h6 {Controls g5} (6... e5 7. Re1 $11) 7. d3 (7. h3 Bxf3
8. Qxf3 e6 $14) 7... Nf6 8. Bd2 (8. h3 Bxf3 9. Qxf3 Nd7 $14) 8... Rb8 $11 9. b3
e6 {Covers d5} 10. h3 Bh5 11. g4 Bg6 12. e5 {White threatens to win material:
e5xf6} Nd7 13. exd6 Bxd6 14. Ne4 Bxe4 (14... Bc7 15. Qe2 $11) 15. dxe4 $14 Ne5
16. Bc3 Nxf3+ 17. Qxf3 O-O 18. Rad1 Qc7 19. e5 (19. Qe3 $5 $14 {is worthy of
consideration}) 19... Bxe5 $11 20. Bxe5 Qxe5 21. Qxc6 Rfc8 {Black threatens to
win material: Rc8xc6} (21... Qc3 22. Kg2 $15) 22. Qd7 {White threatens to win
material: Qd7xa7} Qc3 {Black threatens to win material: Qc3xc2. Black forks:
c2+h3} 23. Qxa7 (23. Qd3 $142 $5 {should not be overlooked} Qa5 24. Qe4 $11)
23... Qxh3 $17 24. Rd3 (24. f3 $5 $17) 24... Qxg4+ $19 25. Rg3 Qe4 26. Rd1 (26.
Qe7 Qxc2 27. Qf6 g6 $19) 26... Rb7 27. Qa5 Rbb8 (27... Qxc2 $142 {Black
clearly has the better chances} 28. Qd2 Qxd2 29. Rxd2 Ra7 $19) 28. Qc3 (28. Qa7
Qxc2 29. Rdd3 $19) 28... f6 $4 {ruins a very nice position} (28... g6 $142 $5
$15 {is a viable option}) 29. Qxf6 (29. Rd7 Kh8 30. Rgxg7 Qe1+ 31. Qxe1 Rg8 32.
Rg3 Rxg3+ 33. fxg3 Rg8 34. Qxe6 Rxg3+ 35. Kf2 Rg6 36. Qd6 Rg2+ 37. Kxg2 Kg8 38.
Qb8#) 29... g5 $4 (29... Rc7 $142 {was a good chance to save the game} 30. Qxh6
Qxc2 31. Qxe6+ Rf7 $14) 30. Rd7 Qe1+ 31. Kh2 (31. Kg2 Qe4+ 32. Kh2 Qh7 33. Rxh7
Kxh7 34. Qf7+ Kh8 35. Rh3 Rf8 36. Rxh6#) 31... Qxf2+ 32. Qxf2 Rf8 33. Rf3 (33.
Qe3 Rf2+ 34. Qxf2 Rf8 35. Qe3 Rf6 36. Rxg5+ hxg5 37. Qxg5+ Kf8 38. Qxf6+ Ke8
39. Qf7#) 33... g4 (33... Rfd8 {doesn't do any good} 34. Qd2 Rxd7 35. Qxd7 Rf8
36. Qxe6+ Kg7 37. Qe7+ Kg6 38. Qxf8 Kh5 39. Rh3+ Kg4 40. Qf3#) 34. Rxf8+ (34.
Rff7 Rfe8 35. Rg7+ Kh8 36. Rh7+ Kg8 37. Rdg7#) 34... Rxf8 35. Qxf8+ (35. Qe2
g3+ 36. Kh3 Rf7 37. Qxe6 h5 38. Qxf7+ Kh8 39. Rd8#) 35... Kxf8 36. Kg3 Ke8 (
36... h5 {is no salvation} 37. Rh7 Ke8 38. a4 Kd8 39. Rxh5 Kc7 40. Rxc5+ Kd6
41. Rc4 e5 42. a5 e4 43. a6 e3 44. a7 e2 45. Re4 Kc7 46. a8=Q e1=R 47. Qa7+ Kd6
48. Rxe1 Kc6 49. Re6+ Kd5 50. Qa6 Kd4 51. Qc4#) 37. Rh7 (37. Rh7 e5 38. a4 Kd8
39. Kxg4 h5+ 40. Kf5 e4 41. Kxe4 Kc8 42. a5 h4 43. a6 Kb8 44. a7+ Ka8 45. Kd5
h3 46. Kc6 h2 47. Kb6 h1=Q 48. Rxh1 c4 49. Rh8#) 1-0

