Qd4 h6 25. Nb6 Rc5 26. Qd1 {1/2-1/2 (26) Hammer,J (2633)-Bezgodov,A (2485)
Khanty-Mansiysk 2010}) (12. e4 Nxe4 13. Nxe6 Qxe6 14. Bxe7 Nxc3 15. Rxc3 Nxe7
$14) 12... bxc6 $11 {Black has new hanging pawns: c6+d5} 13. Na4 Rab8 14. a3 {
Prevents intrusion on b4} h6 {Black threatens to win material: h6xg5} 15. Be3
Rfc8 16. b4 {Black has a new backward pawn: c6} Rb7 17. Bd4 Qd6 (17... Rb5 18.
Qd2 $14) 18. Nc5 $16 Rbc7 19. Qd3 Qd8 20. Rc3 (20. Nxe6 fxe6 21. Bh3 Qd7 $16)
20... Nd7 (20... Bxc5 $5 21. Bxc5 Rd7 $14) 21. Nxe6 fxe6 22. Qe3 e5 23. Bxe5
Nxe5 24. Qxe5 Bf6 25. Qe6+ Kh8 26. Rd3 (26. Rc2 $5 Re7 27. Qg4 Rec7 $18) 26...
Re7 $16 27. Qg4 Qc7 $2 (27... Qe8 28. e3 $16) 28. e3 (28. Rc1 $5 Rce8 29. Bxd5
Rxe2 30. Rxc6 Qe5 $18) 28... Rce8 29. Rfd1 a5 (29... Qb8 30. Qg6 Re5 31. h4 $18
) 30. Rc1 (30. b5 $5 cxb5 31. Rxd5 b4 32. axb4 axb4 $18) 30... Qb6 31. Rc5 (31.
