34... Be7 $5 35. Rc1 Ra8 $16) 35. Rxc6 $18 Rb1+ 36. Bf1 dxe3 37. Rxe3 Rd8 (
37... Rxe3 38. fxe3 Ra1 39. Ra6 $18) 38. Kg2 Rd2 $4 {sad, but how else could
