material: Re1xe7} Qd6 21. Re4 Re8 (21... b5 22. c5 Qd7 23. Rbe1 $11) 22. Rbe1 (
22. Rxb7 $142 $1 Rf8 23. Rxb8 Rxb8 24. g3 $16) 22... Rxe4 $11 23. Rxe4 Qh6 {
Black has a mate threat} 24. Re3 Qd6 25. Qg3 Qxg3 26. Rxg3 {A rook endgame
occured} Rd8 {Black threatens to win material: Rd8xd4} 27. Rd3 f5 28. f4 Kf7
29. Kf2 b5 30. cxb5 cxb5 {White has a new passed pawn: d4.} 31. Ke3 Re8+ 32.
Kf3 Re4 {The black rook on an outpost} 33. g4 (33. Rb3 Rxd4 34. Rxb5 Rd3+ 35.
Kf2 Rxa3 36. Rxf5+ Ke6 $11) 33... g6 (33... Ke6 34. d5+ Kd6 35. gxf5 $15) 34.
