Rd5 {White threatens to win material: Rd5xb5. White forks: b5+f5} Ra4 {Black
threatens to win material: Ra4xa3} 38. Rxb5 Kxd6 (38... Rxa3+ $5 {might be a
viable alternative} 39. Kg2 Kxd6 40. Rxf5 Ke6 $11) 39. Rxf5 $14 Rxa3+ 40. Kg4
a5 41. h4 (41. Rh5 Ra1 $16) 41... Ra1 42. Kh5 (42. Kg5 a4 $14) 42... a4 43. Ra5
